      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "React 18 + TypeScript + Zustand\n\nScreens:\n• Dashboard • Repositories\n• RepoDetail • PullRequests\n• PRDetail • GitHubIssues\n• GitHubIssueDetail • Settings\n\nComponents:\n• Sidebar • StatCard\n• ActivityFeed • PRCard\n• CommitGraph • StashList\n• LocalChangesPanel\n• CommandPalette • AIPanel\n\nAI Features 「Granite」:\n• Impact Analysis\n• Commit Assistant\n• Stash Annotator\n• Repo Onboarding Brief\n\nState 「Zustand」:\n• useNav • useAIPanel\n• useCommandPalette\n• useLocalChanges • useTheme\n\nStyling:\nVanilla CSS + CSS Variables\nJetBrains Mono font",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "React 18 + TypeScript + Zustand\n\nScreens:\n• Dashboard • Repositories\n• RepoDetail • PullRequests\n• PRDetail • GitHubIssues\n• GitHubIssueDetail • Settings\n\nComponents:\n• Sidebar • StatCard\n• ActivityFeed • PRCard\n• CommitGraph • StashList\n• LocalChangesPanel\n• CommandPalette • AIPanel\n\nAI Features 「Granite」:\n• Impact Analysis\n• Commit Assistant\n• Stash Annotator\n• Repo Onboarding Brief\n\nState 「Zustand」:\n• useNav • useAIPanel\n• useCommandPalette\n• useLocalChanges • useTheme\n\nStyling:\nVanilla CSS + CSS Variables\nJetBrains Mono font",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 415,
      "autoResize": true
